Sick and Shut-in

The following is our list of sick and shut-in. Feel free to send them a letter of encouragement or pay them a visit. When you know that others care, it lifts one's spirit. More than anything else; keep them in your prayers.

Sister Minnie Dozier

Sister Janet Lee
Deaconess Olive Banks
Sister Katie Lake
Brother Ephraim Lake
Sister Louise Farrow
Sister Grace Etheridge
Sister Florence Frazier
Brother Earl Mims
Sister Fern Haulcy

Sister Grace Etheridge

Sister Marlene Arline

Sister Annie James

Sister Emma Bland

Sister Verona Robinson
